oai_dc:dc.dc:title: George Franklin Robinson hand-drawn map of Army of Northern Virginia's march to and from Gettysburg, Pennsylvania
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Map of G. F. Robinson unit's (and the Army of Northern Virginia's) march from Fredericksburg, Virginia, to Gettysburg, Pennsylvania and back to Virginia. See TSLA Mf. 1969 for all G. F. Robinson letters.
